So was the work of the road that identified the body of Alfonso Cano
A Lofoscopist from Cali went to history as the man who confirmed the death of "Alfonso Cano".
The work of these officials is key.
Last November 4 a CTI Lofoscopist from Cali passed on to history as the man who confirmed the identity of the highest leader of the Farc: "Alfonso Cano", through the collection of his fingerprints.
Of the seven locoscopists working in the ITC section, this week it was the turn of "availability" to Eliaszar González, a man from Puerto Tejada who has been working in the judicial investigation area for 21 years.
At the start of his career, González worked in municipalities of the Chocó, where he often had to stay in the forest for more than five days to get to the place where the bodies were to be identified.
In 2000, he moved to the capital of the Valley and, after conducting the corresponding courses, specialized in lofoscopy, which is the study of the hair of the friction, i.e. palm of his hands and feet.
The week of operation against Alfonso Cano's aliases told him to wear minimum clothes for three days.
Something big was waiting for him.
Friday night came out for the Cauca on a helicopter from Palmira.
He knew that he had to identify two bodies and that one of them was suspected of being the man who led the oldest guerrilla in the world, so they asked him to carry the decadactic card of Guillermo Leon Sáenz (his real name).
However, when he arrived with the research team at the site where the body was located, he did not recognize it because it was very different from what he had seen in the media.
I was without beard, dressed as a peasant in the area, without glasses and much more delicate.
But the prints don't lie.
Accompanied by a galtonian lupa, ink, a transplanter and a flashlight, Eliezer compared the fingerprints of the body to those of the card.
His eye did not fail: it was Alfonso Cano.
That same night, the man from Puerto Tejada was responsible for confirming to the Minister of Defence Juan Carlos Pinzón, who was, in fact, the chief of the Farc.
Searching for track
For a doctiloscopist from Sijin de Cali, the recognition made by President Juan Manuel Santos to Elias González, in the press wheel by the operation against Cano, is very significant.
A lot of people don't know our work.
Dactyloscopy is an accurate science, without error, that can become a key in crime resolution.
In addition to the identification of corpses, locoscopists support investigations into crimes such as theft and murder and confirm the identity of the captured persons.
When caught, many offenders present false notes or do not have papers.
We take their fingerprints and search them in the database.
The investigator told him that, in a case of theft, he had to remove a piece of wall from a house, because in that place the thief had supported his hand to pull out a strong box full of jewelry and money.
"The walls are difficult because they are not suitable surfaces to print a fingerprint, but in that case we were able to obtain the fingerprint of the whole hand and identify the offender, who had participated in different thefts," he recalled.
The marks can also dismiss or confirm suspects in cases of murder.
They recently found a dead man with bottles of liquor around him.
The investigation found that a family member could be suspected of the crime and, in fact, a trace in the bottle coincided.
Although this does not guarantee that he was the killer, he does place him on the scene of the crime.
A CTI dactyloscope explained that in the objects "the traces are removed with chemical or physical reagents".
When they appear, a transplanter or tape is used to lift them.
After this, the impressions are sent to Asif, which is the criminal database, or to the Registry.
"The problem is that there are still many undocumented Colombians," said ITC expert.
He made it clear that not everything is as shown in the CSI television program.
Just as not everything that shines is gold, not everything that touches becomes a mark.
However, if it can be used, if the respective quota is made.
